OL,3,CNew support group targets men as
OL,4,Csuicide deaths reach worst-ever level
OL,6,FA new support group is trying to help
OL,7,Fmen with their mental health - as
OL,8,Ffigures reveal the area now has its
OL,9,Fworst rates of suicide since records
OL,10,Fbegan.
OL,12,FA total of 162 deaths were recorded in
OL,13,FWigan between 2022 and 2024 - the
OL,14,Fhighest in the 20 years records have
OL,15,Fbeen kept and far above the national
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,18,FThose behind support group, Epic Men,
OL,19,Fsay they know how difficult life can
OL,20,Fbe during the festive and post-festive
OL,21,Ftime of year.
