OL,3,CNew support group targets men as
OL,4,Csuicide deaths reach worst-ever level
OL,6,FThe group's Peter Gregory told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "Four years ago - Christmas - I
OL,8,Fwas very down and I Googled how to
OL,9,Fkill myself.
OL,11,F"I've learned strategies now to know
OL,12,Fthose lighter days do come.
OL,14,F"It doesn't feel like it, at the time,
OL,15,Fbut they do come."
OL,17,FHe added: "If there weren't these
OL,18,Fgroups, it doesn't bear thinking about
OL,19,Fwhat the statistics would be.
