OL,3,CNew support group targets men as
OL,4,Csuicide deaths reach worst-ever level
OL,6,F"But the more groups we have, the
OL,7,Fbetter possibility we have of helping
OL,8,Fpeople (and) preventing death by
OL,9,Fsuicides."
OL,11,FThe new group is part of a wider
OL,12,Forganisation, dedicated to suicide
OL,13,Fprevention.
OL,15,FEPiC HOPE already run groups known as
OL,16,FCrisis Harbours, for anyone struggling
OL,17,Fwith their mental health.
