OL,3,CNew support group targets men as
OL,4,Csuicide deaths reach worst-ever level
OL,6,FThanks to funding from the community,
OL,7,Fthey can now go directly to those who
OL,8,Fneed help with a van that drives to
OL,9,Fsuicide hotspots to intervene before
OL,10,Fit is too late.
OL,12,FEllie Palma-Cass, CEO of EPiC Hope,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This van does save lives.
OL,15,F"It's saved countless lives. We've
OL,16,Fbeen going out literally every day in
OL,17,Fthe van.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
