OL,3,CNew support group targets men as
OL,4,Csuicide deaths reach worst-ever level
OL,6,F"The sad thing is, the public hear
OL,7,Fabout these numbers going up but they
OL,8,Fdon't hear about the lives that are
OL,9,Fbeing saved.
OL,11,F"We're always trying to spread that
OL,12,Fgood news as well, that actually we've
OL,13,Freached over 1,100 people in this year.
OL,15,F"People need to hear that good news.
OL,16,FThat's lives that have been saved.
OL,18,F"We don't want to lose anybody to
OL,19,Fsuicide."
